Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜,安靜,安靜,\N怎麼又吵鬧了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說過一百次要排隊喝水的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他霸佔了水杯不讓我喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,水缸都要倒下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他說謊,他想潑水在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓,我沒潑水,他說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Senhor, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,好了,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喝水結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜回教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老...老...師,我好渴,我想喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師,我沒喝到水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,要喝水的安靜來這裡站好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一年級站第一排...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,水缸裡的水不夠大家喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去溪裡喝嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜,大家都有喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喝過的回教室, 知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,水缸破了,水流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師,水流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你看,這裡破了,水流出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,噢,水缸破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜,退後,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,說,誰打破的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,誰幹的?說實話...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,帶過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你們笑什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你跑什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼好怕的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為水缸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他們打破想怪在我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?你口袋裡是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你藏著什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一把彈弓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拿過來,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拿過來,沒聽見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看.拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我說拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你口袋裡是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你麻煩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你用彈弓打破了水缸還想跑,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不老師,我發誓沒打破水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是打鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有打破水缸跑什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他們就是想怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Arna,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他射得好準
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只是這樣說,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我能說嗎,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒見到他射水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他彈弓不離手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我發誓.我沒射水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我發誓.我沒打破水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們只是愛瞎說,他們亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想看到你帶著彈弓,好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,大概是自己破掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,去年有個水缸 晚上還好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到了早上就裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠裡晚上很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,村裡有誰會修水缸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,誰呢, Kazempour
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary的爸爸,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,給他,他能修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去年,醋缸破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary的爸爸來修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary,回家看看你爸爸在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要他來學校一趟, 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他不在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,去啊,也許在呢. 孩子們...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大家進教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去,用跑的,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,盡早回來,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,習題作了沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很好, Jafary,你也做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我爸爸不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼去這麼久?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,從早上到現在?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我家在村子的那一頭,很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他去了前村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,幫 Yadollah 先生下種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他說不行,他很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他有空才來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,回教室,去做算數題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他爸爸不願意來,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他爸爸要錢 他不會白幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亂講,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸不愛錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他今天有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他明天來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我看他來不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回教室去...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在背後說別人閒話是不好的,\N明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,孩子們要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他們要出去做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他們要去溪邊喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喝水...好吧,但是小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別推擠到水裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧...別吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小心別跌到水裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,別拿石頭丟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰啊? 是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是我們 Gholamhosin 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老師和我, 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎,真是稀客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什麼壞事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是壞事,我們是來請你幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請進...去,上床去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,難得光臨寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,起來,起來, 你老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidy 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ghanbary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,十分歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,光臨寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,別打擾孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一會兒就走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,請原諒這麼晚來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喔,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,學校的水缸破了 孩子們都等著用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你會修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明天可以請你來一趟嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不老師,誰說我會修的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他哪知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,修這個可沒那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,需要工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不如買個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,總之,修它既困難又不耐用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,政府應該給你買個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要政府送個新的來要好長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,況且附近也沒有賣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不如請你過去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是可以修?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要是修好了你可幫了孩子們大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟,你的孩子也在那裡唸書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這幾天我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也許下個星期我去修好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我不能放下手邊的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不能耽擱一天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,難得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這位先生來到這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,學校的孩子們喝不到水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓先生很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想想我的工作和生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只是瞎說一氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爸,為什麼不去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要那樣說?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我說什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好多事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,總不能耽誤正事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,免費去學校修水缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不工作你哪來吃的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你也許可以一大早先去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕老師會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最後把孩子趕出學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,首先,他不會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我就帶著他去上工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣他也能學些東西\N他的課業也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你再哭下去,我要教訓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒臉明天去見老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你去學校是為了學習還是為了去看老師的臉色?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還不快去睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爸,去修水缸吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟你說多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去別人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把工作做完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要收麥子冬天才有得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他們說了你會去修的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該那麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你說之前應該先問過我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去上學吧,你會遲到的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去上學,要遲到了, 去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, Ghanbary 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了? 去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ismaiel,去他家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要他立刻來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他說他爸爸不來沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他說要是他不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我要自己來找他的 知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobra 太太,Ghanbary 在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不在,他上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他逃學了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,逃學?為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸不來學校修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他覺得丟臉所以逃學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我說破了嘴那人也不肯去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現在人家把他兒子趕出了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他該得到教訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,忙什麼, Kobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Abmad 不知怎麼逃學了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有看見他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,會找到的,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌,他餓了就會回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,乘多少,為什麼是 7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,3乘7得 21
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不對...應該是 8
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok,擦掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你上哪去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我一下子就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒允許就離開學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我去讓我爸來修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼好笑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好了坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸不來沒關係的,知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,下次別不假外出了好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧,你爸沒來你得自己修水缸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就說你爸不會免費修的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,四年級安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebrahimy,你不放過低年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,現在又去打擾五年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼這麼吵?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, Abdollahy,回座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,五年級生,抄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚回家做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary,有見到 lsmaiely 嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,他沒來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓他去你家找你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把孩子趕出學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你說多少次你就是不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把孩子趕出學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,趕出學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說他怕丟臉就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是他老師說了什麼他覺得丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看我怎麼對付他老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他應該去找孩子回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老師沒說他什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是他自己逃學的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜小心我打斷你的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,非教訓你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了,先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這是學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣,學校,去他的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別打他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜,他爹...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至少對不起老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別打他.別打他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他做了什麼要你這樣對他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼折磨他?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓他打你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓他在打他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你回家看我怎麼整你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你終究要回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還以為他是來修水缸的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是來打孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahmads的爸爸有時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,自己也不知道為什麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,請原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請尊重學校秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的水缸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒法可想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊...還有那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了,這邊裂了,這裡破了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,無法可想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,全破了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能稍稍修一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能弄些爐灰...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很多的石灰和蛋青
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也許可以試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可以將它綁緊些嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那需要工具,需要繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,需要鑽洞的鑽子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.73,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,需要繩索固定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它老舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多年的夏熱冬冷損害了它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你找齊了我說的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:22:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,石灰,蛋青和爐灰,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也許可以幫你試試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有可能修的囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看老天的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候可以準備好這些東西呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,希望是下個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這星期就是下星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了你們都回教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,回教室,快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都看見 Ghanbary的爸爸要幫學校修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為了這個,他需要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一些石灰,爐灰還有蛋青
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明天大家帶一些乾淨的爐灰石灰和蛋來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師, 老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是誰能帶就帶些來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,現在安靜回家...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爸,Ghanbary 先生要幫學校修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟老師說要我們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帶爐灰,石灰和蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想帶蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.40,0:24:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我們連吃的雞蛋都沒有你還想帶去學校修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.61,0:24:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的孩子都要帶東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.61,0:24:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不帶會丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.36,0:25:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 給不給嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,聽不懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.94,0:25:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要帶什麼去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.14,0:25:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看見這些爐灰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.77,0:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只有爐灰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,爐灰你要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去做功課了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.00,0:25:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,石灰或爐灰,還是你都要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.14,0:25:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,喔不,如果碰石灰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.34,0:25:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我會弄傷手弄瞎眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.74,0:25:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.81,0:25:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就是沒雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.33,0:26:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我帶什麼去學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,明天你沒什麼可帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.44,0:26:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,別人會帶石灰,雞蛋和爐灰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.21,0:26:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.48,0:26:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我為什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.75,0:26:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.35,0:26:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,帶爐灰吧,爐灰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.98,0:26:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要爐灰,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.18,0:26:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要,等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.99,0:26:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你也等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.59,0:26:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不放羊了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.06,0:26:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看我打斷你的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天去學校說去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.79,0:26:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼學校,整天要東要西的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.53,0:26:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,政府應該買水缸的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.53,0:26:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我去學校說去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.03,0:26:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他們說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.67,0:26:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你整天只會找麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.78,0:26:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.88,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你喜歡,晚上給你煮幾個雞蛋吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,或是讓你帶去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.46,0:27:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不高興?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.86,0:27:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸答應修水缸了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要帶東西去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.30,0:27:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別人會帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.57,0:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你再惹毛你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.00,0:27:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他不去修水缸了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你會在別的孩子面前丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.04,0:27:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,說 我好丟臉,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.84,0:27:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我好丟臉.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡面的雞蛋是你拿了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.22,0:27:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是,我要帶去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.75,0:27:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,用蛋青修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨天不是帶了些雞蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.66,0:27:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼又要雞蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有帶去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.73,0:28:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:28:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看你們弄得一團糟.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.03,0:29:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.90,0:29:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了乾淨的石灰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.64,0:29:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了爐灰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.14,0:29:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,誰要你們帶這麼多石灰和爐灰的?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.04,0:29:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得一團亂?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.55,0:29:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你們自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.30,0:29:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我有說倒在自己身上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.38,0:29:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yea?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.99,0:29:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我帶了雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.62,0:29:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, 我帶了雞蛋可是路上打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.29,0:29:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好,你先拿著...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.64,0:29:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還有誰帶雞蛋的?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.09,0:29:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.29,0:29:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你也先拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.60,0:29:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是請 Ghanbary去問他爸爸四個雞蛋夠嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.08,0:29:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.12,0:29:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,四個顯然是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家把帶來的東西放在水缸旁邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.24,0:30:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小心放好...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.43,0:30:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明天不要再帶爐灰和石灰了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.22,0:30:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要是可能的話,帶雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.02,0:30:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.06,0:30:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去,去,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.05,0:30:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,起立!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.05,0:30:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就坐,孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.86,0:30:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我幾時要你們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.39,0:30:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,帶這麼多石灰和爐灰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.23,0:30:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看你們把自己和學校弄成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.58,0:30:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要更多的雞蛋,要帶就帶雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.45,0:30:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我們...我們...我們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有生蛋的母雞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.17,0:30:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.88,0:30:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我們也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.04,0:30:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣吧,帶雞蛋來的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.09,0:30:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,美術課可以得 A
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.82,0:30:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可以在雞蛋上畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.34,0:31:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要生的雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.44,0:31:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.63,0:31:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Zynab 太太,有沒有雞蛋\N好讓我們家Hossein帶去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.97,0:31:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zynab 太太!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.34,0:31:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是要帶去學校吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.06,0:31:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不,不是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.35,0:31:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那要幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.21,0:31:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,為了美術課
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.44,0:31:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,沒有,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.43,0:32:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,爸,你可以畫隻看起來像馬的驢子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.31,0:33:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.27,0:33:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在蛋上畫驢子畫馬的?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.64,0:33:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老師說在雞蛋上畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.18,0:33:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會,你自己想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.27,0:33:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有彩色筆
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.67,0:33:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼畫?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道,用粉筆加上墨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.32,0:33:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼問我?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.67,0:33:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去問你老師
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.32,0:33:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.83,0:33:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼打驢子,你有病啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.80,0:33:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.20,0:33:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這裡有 15個雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有些畫得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.69,0:33:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有些則非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.04,0:33:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.36,0:33:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有帶雞蛋的美術課會不會得F?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.06,0:33:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不會,他們有其他的事可做
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.50,0:33:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老師...我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.68,0:33:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我等了好久可是母雞就是不生蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.85,0:33:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸給我兩里奧要我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.57,0:33:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要錢,回到隊伍裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.86,0:33:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.58,0:33:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你收集了許多雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.35,0:33:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝神
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.33,0:34:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋青拿去修水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.35,0:34:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你就有蛋黃吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.74,0:34:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.55,0:34:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rahmany,誰教你這麼說的?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.58,0:34:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起頭來說你從哪學來這些話的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.75,0:34:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我只是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.92,0:34:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.72,0:34:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是家裡有人這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.33,0:34:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你拿回你的蛋,知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.54,0:34:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我知道誰教的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.40,0:34:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸最小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.31,0:34:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你安靜,沒人問你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.86,0:34:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.25,0:34:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,帶雞蛋來的人都把蛋拿會去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:34:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經登記了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.99,0:35:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給美術課打上分數
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你不修水缸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.43,0:35:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我可以叫我爸來修水缸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.01,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了,大家把機蛋拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.95,0:35:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家還等什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不需要雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.37,0:35:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我不拿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.24,0:35:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不拿回去的,明天不要來了,明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.64,0:36:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誰的雞蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誰的雞蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.21,0:36:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.69,0:38:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請原諒我,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.76,0:38:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請原諒我,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.56,0:38:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我把雞蛋放這兒好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,老師來了,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.38,0:38:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.28,0:38:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福你!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.64,0:38:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我說老師
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.77,0:38:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.48,0:38:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不該像我們老頭這麼容易上火
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.11,0:38:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不必瞞我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.50,0:38:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們從學校回來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.85,0:38:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,說你很不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.66,0:39:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Abbas Ali 的孩子說的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.11,0:39:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,其實,很多無聊事你不必當真的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.04,0:39:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是為了蛋黃的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gholamhosin 什麼時候去修水缸啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.17,0:39:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.86,0:39:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.85,0:39:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰啊?來了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.87,0:39:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.64,0:39:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.72,0:39:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.86,0:39:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不了,很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.93,0:39:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以來修水缸了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.60,0:39:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,需要的東西都齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.65,0:39:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,後天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.07,0:39:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.25,0:39:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還有,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.46,0:39:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你今天很生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.98,0:40:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再見,你來學校時再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.83,0:40:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我想跟你說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.70,0:40:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要說的是你別把孩子們的話放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.50,0:40:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.64,0:40:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.20,0:40:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啦,那是家長的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.54,0:40:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是爸爸說的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.28,0:40:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子哪曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.78,0:40:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼蛋青蛋黃的事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.55,0:40:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你為孩子們很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.35,0:40:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.39,0:40:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.19,0:40:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕要遲了,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.72,0:40:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.06,0:40:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,忙什麼呢,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.37,0:40:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.87,0:40:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫大家說說心裡話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.35,0:40:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你為了孩子們這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.62,0:40:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不值四個雞蛋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你看來有點虛,該吃點蛋補補
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.66,0:40:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.89,0:40:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,當我聽我兒子說
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.46,0:40:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你為 Abbas Ali家的孩子說的話生氣時
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.48,0:40:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我氣得給了他一巴掌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.18,0:40:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他別再去別處亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.92,0:41:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.79,0:41:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,上哪去啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.老師
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.26,0:41:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我到處找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.61,0:41:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,學校也去了,你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.83,0:41:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有你城理來的包裹和信
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.68,0:41:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我放在你房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.42,0:41:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我給水壺裝滿了水
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.21,0:41:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,房間也掃了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.01,0:41:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,茶也準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.06,0:41:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你,你做得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.29,0:41:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,Gholambosin幾時去修水缸?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.70,0:41:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,東西準備好他就來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.23,0:41:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天, 村子裡都在談論你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.17,0:41:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.64,0:41:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahmood,請別再談今天的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.85,0:42:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.02,0:42:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為不想獨居
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.05,0:42:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你和村裡一個年輕人同住
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.94,0:42:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這很好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.93,0:42:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你寄了果醬和餅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.96,0:42:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還寄了襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.17,0:42:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.37,0:42:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們知道你很好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.20,0:42:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,還有,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.23,0:42:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有發薪水嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.31,0:43:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.97,0:43:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還要點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.72,0:43:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不了,我吃過晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.75,0:43:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.44,0:43:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還有啊,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.67,0:43:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大間都知道 Abbas Ali Rahmany 是吝嗇鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.74,0:43:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他會這麼教他兒子說話
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.81,0:43:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了, Mahmood
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.53,0:43:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為水缸能修好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.41,0:43:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.23,0:43:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是這裡的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.02,0:43:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是老師,我還真想喝喝這水缸裡的水
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喝著這水缸裡的水,會讓我覺得像個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.69,0:43:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有上過學嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.42,0:43:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.20,0:43:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不可以幫我去學校當領班?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.85,0:44:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahmood,你明天叫孩子們帶烤餅來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.18,0:44:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,烤餅?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.20,0:44:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,對,只要手掌這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.09,0:44:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要告訴兩三個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.96,0:44:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人就會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.02,0:44:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, Kazemy 在吃餅
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.80,0:44:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過,等一下.先別吃...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.81,0:44:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 誰來說說
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.31,0:44:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gholamhosin來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.55,0:44:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gholamhosin 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.95,0:44:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的, OK
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.63,0:45:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.83,0:45:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.47,0:45:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別推
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.77,0:45:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他工作,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.88,0:45:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.11,0:45:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我會容易些
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.41,0:45:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,退後,大家退後
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.14,0:45:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去拿雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.32,0:45:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去拿...等一下,這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.36,0:45:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要一個去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.44,0:45:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary, 你去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.99,0:45:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazemy, 你去拿火盆
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.46,0:45:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小心別把油濺出來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.67,0:45:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,lsmaiely,你去拿油罐
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.30,0:45:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鍋子和杓
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.15,0:45:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,別忘了底盆
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.57,0:45:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人過來,快
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.66,0:46:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.53,0:46:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,給自己做午餐嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.63,0:46:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老師老師
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.69,0:46:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是要當大家面吃蛋黃
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.38,0:46:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們,大家過來,一個跟一個
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.15,0:46:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子先
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.78,0:46:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,帶著你們的餅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.93,0:46:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一年級的先來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,給你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.28,0:47:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,爸,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.13,0:47:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你自己不吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.97,0:47:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒味道.沒有鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.91,0:47:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去說...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.61,0:47:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師,你沒放鹽,沒味道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.30,0:47:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手藝不好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.55,0:47:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去我房裡拿鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.12,0:47:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我的已經吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.59,0:47:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係.很好,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.71,0:47:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyla,去吧 他去拿鹽了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.90,0:48:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,好少喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你給一年級的比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.47,0:48:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼給我這麼少?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.82,0:48:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都得分一些,好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.13,0:48:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.82,0:48:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我怎麼辦,只吃餅嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.19,0:48:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,lsmaiely,你來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.10,0:48:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,隊伍排好等我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.77,0:48:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,排好隊,別亂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.49,0:48:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你還沒吃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.10,0:48:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃過了,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.17,0:48:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.39,0:48:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老師馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.84,0:48:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.85,0:48:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,lsmaiely,回你位置去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.52,0:48:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們別亂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.35,0:48:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只有沒吃到蛋的可以上前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.55,0:48:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,果醬,沒吃蛋的好幸運喔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.49,0:48:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃過了,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.23,0:49:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.13,0:49:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.10,0:49:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不餓...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.36,0:49:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們大家回教室
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.17,0:49:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,下來,你會再把它打破的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.04,0:49:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, 我好渴
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.31,0:49:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可以給水缸加水嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.46,0:49:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不能放水
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.43,0:49:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得先讓它乾了硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.06,0:49:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看見我剛修好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.45,0:49:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我好渴,怎麼喝水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.48,0:49:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的工作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.45,0:49:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老師還有其他的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.93,0:49:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.73,0:49:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.65,0:49:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, 我可了, 怎麼喝水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.51,0:49:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼喝那麼多水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.02,0:49:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃了什麼要喝那麼多水?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.74,0:50:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我吃了果醬和蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.59,0:50:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,排隊去溪邊喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.03,0:50:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快點回來,好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.20,0:50:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快點喝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.33,0:50:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.89,0:50:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別喝太多!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.52,0:50:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,會肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.43,0:50:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好涼啊,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.27,0:50:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,過來,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.47,0:50:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.93,0:50:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,噢,老天
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.37,0:51:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.89,0:51:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你會感冒的,看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.70,0:51:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告訴老師
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.75,0:51:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事,手拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.85,0:51:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一漂走了怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.93,0:51:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沈下去你就好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.67,0:51:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,暖和嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要用毯子蓋住你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.04,0:51:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.74,0:51:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是老師的午餐來賓之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.76,0:51:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我說去教室,沒你們什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.01,0:52:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走開,走...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.19,0:52:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.26,0:52:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼還不走?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.83,0:52:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.65,0:52:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子起身
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把藥喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,起身把藥喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.49,0:52:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再喝點水
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.63,0:52:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,水缸滿了,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.67,0:52:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要來看一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.29,0:53:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老師水缸滿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.79,0:53:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們裝滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.56,0:53:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼把自己弄濕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.38,0:53:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.69,0:53:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary 先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.94,0:53:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他爸爸比誰都辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.35,0:53:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.42,0:53:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老師應該先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.89,0:53:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.46,0:53:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不孩子們, 你們應該先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.99,0:53:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你先喝, 你先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.96,0:53:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你先喝,你先喝
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.72,0:54:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好,好, 我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.90,0:54:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師,下面有水流出來,看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.57,0:54:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.37,0:54:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,水缸的底是破的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.97,0:54:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,底破了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.45,0:54:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋青都浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.41,0:54:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.91,0:54:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,現在怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.51,0:54:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們,水缸沒修好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.75,0:54:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.97,0:54:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須等教育局給我們送個新的來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.66,0:54:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.47,0:54:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要耽誤課業...去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.70,0:54:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dara
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.27,0:54:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dara
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.87,0:54:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomegranate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.00,0:54:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomegranate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.07,0:54:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.51,0:54:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.41,0:54:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dara
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.18,0:54:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dara
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.74,0:54:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomegranate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pomegranate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.91,0:54:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.08,0:54:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.25,0:54:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喂.老師
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.68,0:54:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.49,0:54:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子喝水掉到溪裡.是他們推的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.71,0:54:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他發了一天一夜的燒到早上才睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.36,0:55:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是掉進井裡那還得了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.95,0:55:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人推他是他自己掉進溪裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.80,0:55:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不買個水缸呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.97,0:55:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我還能怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.70,0:55:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我寫了信給教育局要他們買個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.46,0:55:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.42,0:55:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果政府不買
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.21,0:55:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們自己出錢買一個
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.85,0:55:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們收錢.我叫我兒子去城裡買一個
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.64,0:55:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好讓孩子們喝得到水
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.62,0:55:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊,這對孩子們和我都是樁好事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.60,0:55:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.61,0:55:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.87,0:55:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等著瞧囉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.78,0:55:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我沒錢買嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.44,0:55:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你相不相信:我下星期就買一個來?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.91,0:55:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等著瞧囉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.73,0:55:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我會買的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.78,0:55:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手腳又沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.13,0:55:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定會買的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.92,0:55:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Narges,你好,好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.65,0:55:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Kavar,好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.41,0:55:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,學校的水缸破了 孩子們沒水喝
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.62,0:55:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼帶著孩子們到處轉...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.35,0:56:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我來找你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.05,0:56:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒錢,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.13,0:56:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你有的話給一些
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.47,0:56:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我先生去城裡找工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.16,0:56:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多少就給我一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.20,0:56:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸吧看見會罰我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.10,0:56:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不會給我什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.98,0:56:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事, Kavar?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.69,0:56:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你孩子不上學嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.22,0:56:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,學校的水缸破了,幫個忙我們要買新的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.67,0:56:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別煩我 我不善於理財的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.63,0:56:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,誰說的?你有兩塊農地
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.30,0:56:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,別跟我乞討
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.05,0:56:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,給我們五個脫曼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.17,0:56:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,五個脫曼!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.80,0:56:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你是老師還是村長啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.71,0:56:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,政府應該自己去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.23,0:56:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把手伸進口帶,閉上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.03,0:56:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,心理想著神
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.50,0:57:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能給多少就給多少
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.38,0:57:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不給我是不會離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.95,0:57:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著這兩個脫曼帶著孩子們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.04,0:57:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過會拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.13,0:57:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.92,0:57:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是在幹什麼啊, Khavar?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.22,0:57:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在村裡引起了大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.02,0:57:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這村子沒有長者了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.36,0:57:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,村裡沒有村長了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.38,0:57:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是,村裡有長著和村長
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.12,0:57:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是學校沒有水缸
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.67,0:57:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,學校有沒有水缸關你什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.13,0:57:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼強迫村民?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.73,0:57:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼發瘋?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.67,0:58:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是那年輕老師忽弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.89,0:58:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不會亂搞...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.79,0:58:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人忽弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.56,0:58:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒強迫別人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.33,0:58:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他們愛給多少是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.37,0:58:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你說你要為學校的水缸出多少錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.11,0:58:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.91,0:58:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.68,0:58:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在啊,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.08,0:58:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.25,0:58:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是受過教育的明白人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.42,0:58:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼做這種糊塗事?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.68,0:58:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.85,0:58:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你想還能發生什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.35,0:58:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是壞女人 你不清楚她
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.82,0:58:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她不壞,她工作認真
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.79,0:58:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她一向喜歡助人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.76,0:59:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她很單純 有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.13,0:59:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓她滿村子跑找村民要錢有道理嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.10,0:59:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.94,0:59:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒叫她做...她自己自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.76,0:59:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她自己不清楚怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.85,0:59:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,人們會說她的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.58,0:59:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會說她是為自己牟利
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.82,0:59:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這樣你還會這樣做嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.56,0:59:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓孩子們暫時用桶子喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.48,0:59:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把它放在學校旁邊 給孩子們喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.11,0:59:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.72,0:59:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那桶子都鏽爛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.70,0:59:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是洞
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.77,0:59:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們用它取水到學校都只剩半桶了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.31,0:59:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,況且錫是有危險的\N孩子們在上面推擠
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.74,0:59:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一喝水弄破了嘴或唇\N怎麼向父母交代?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.88,0:59:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,總之,你要知道這女人以你之名都在幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.92,0:59:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以我之名?什麼以我之名?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.09,1:00:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以你之名或以學校之名\N反正不好聽就是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.34,1:00:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她不會買什麼水缸的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.18,1:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是告訴你一聲,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.16,1:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,聽不聽在你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.28,1:00:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostafa, Mostafa
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.01,1:00:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是我, Khavar, 開門
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.30,1:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是 Khavar...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.93,1:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一個脫曼
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.53,1:00:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.50,1:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不給也沒關係\N你還要養孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.67,1:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希望那些有錢的大老們有你一半的善心
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.32,1:00:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了女人,走開吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.01,1:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我又沒叫你為了水缸收錢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.08,1:00:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己要做的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.48,1:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要買個水缸放在學校角落
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.12,1:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我真為你們女士們丟臉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.87,1:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,胡鬧夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.76,1:01:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別打擾人家...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.59,1:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們快離開
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.56,1:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼忽弄這個女人?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.96,1:01:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦村長.你自己開口了\N你說你要出多少?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.80,1:01:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不跟瘋女人開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.19,1:01:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,妳愛怎麼怎麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.02,1:01:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好,我們看這瘋女人是不是能給學校弄個水缸
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.22,1:01:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的份子錢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.69,1:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這點錢恐怕不夠幫她買水缸的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.51,1:01:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.93,1:01:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你年輕人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.53,1:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別聽別人的. Khavar一定信守諾言
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.20,1:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mohammad Ali好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.05,1:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mohammad Ali 很好
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.31,1:01:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyed Reza!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.08,1:02:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來買啊!來看看我帶了什麼好東西來.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.18,1:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃,杏仁,草莓
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.45,1:02:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,來買些吧,你會積德的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.02,1:02:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要買個水缸
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.99,1:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為了學校幫個忙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.12,1:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家怕得要死
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.31,1:02:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩來見證
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.23,1:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,免得日後我賣這些東西有人說閒話
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.47,1:02:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不捲入這檔事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.40,1:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你看一眼嘛,只看一眼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.59,1:02:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想捲進去 不會買的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.97,1:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我就帶回家留著.隨人家怎麼說吧.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.69,1:02:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Abbas,去買水缸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.34,1:02:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,孩子們!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.10,1:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Abbas要去買水缸了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.44,1:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.09,1:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,下個星期我會將水缸放在學校裡.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.50,1:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Abbas,帶上錢去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.17,1:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.11,1:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福你...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.16,1:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不對,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.95,1:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要用你的手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.02,1:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,起來坐好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.69,1:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,手洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.19,1:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,起來坐著
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.29,1:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,起來坐著用手喝
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.76,1:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別把水弄渾了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.06,1:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,起來坐著
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.10,1:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用手...不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.20,1:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.15,1:04:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看見他們正在喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.90,1:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把羊趕走
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.55,1:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,瞪著我幹嘛?快趕走.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.18,1:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我怕水
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.62,1:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,來,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.27,1:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過跌過一次而已
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.39,1:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下,別怕
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.09,1:05:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,別飆水,別
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.94,1:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要撥水
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.28,1:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要撥水
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.47,1:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,喝水結束
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.92,1:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明天記得帶杯子來就不必用手了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.93,1:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.65,1:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.98,1:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.79,1:05:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.00,1:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好想喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.56,1:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼? 是酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.49,1:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味,給我們嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.99,1:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我打賭就是水啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.24,1:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我們喝的一樣的水
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.64,1:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把瓶子給我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.34,1:06:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看裡面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.84,1:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.47,1:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.74,1:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.98,1:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.22,1:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你會打破瓶子的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.90,1:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你打破了!你打破了!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.98,1:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我的手,我的手割破了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.21,1:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.18,1:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師 是 Ebrahymy不對
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.45,1:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他去搶 Ghanbary的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.47,1:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你說過多少次別這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.55,1:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.37,1:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,救命,老師救命,哦,我的側邊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.79,1:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,好了.起來.\N傷得重嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.96,1:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你幹的?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.60,1:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,起來.你看他的手
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.84,1:07:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.67,1:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,別擔心.他裝死.他沒事的.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.60,1:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.00,1:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.50,1:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.59,1:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,lsmaiely,去房裡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.49,1:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用水杯放些糖和水,攪拌一下拿來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.41,1:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快去...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.95,1:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,起來,喝了這個
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.45,1:08:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了你會好些
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.09,1:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,來喝吧,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.26,1:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好些嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.98,1:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來是好些了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.26,1:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以起來走嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.07,1:08:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢回家休息
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.24,1:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,別再跟人打架
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.12,1:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他沒帶杯子只帶了腦袋!他想洗澡.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.55,1:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他帶的是桶子不是杯子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.12,1:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的桶子不是喝水的,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.04,1:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為學校帶的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.44,1:08:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這些容器都沒用
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.96,1:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.16,1:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把瓶子,玻璃罐陶罐
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.60,1:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,任何會打破的東西放到走廊角落
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.84,1:09:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們拿什麼喝水呢,老師?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.71,1:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.94,1:09:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在照我的話做然後回教室
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.51,1:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回教室
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.70,1:09:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghanbary,過來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.95,1:09:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.05,1:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還好, 老師
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.95,1:09:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有 Ebrahymy的消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.92,1:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不不,我只想問你知道他家在哪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.05,1:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們住在村子底
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.87,1:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他們靠什麼生活?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.41,1:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他們沒有土地和農地
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.68,1:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他爸爸去城裡打工
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.94,1:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,每年冬天回來
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.03,1:10:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到了春天,他又走了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.60,1:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好,回家時問候你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.85,1:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello,老師 上哪去啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.42,1:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,天氣好.去走走
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.19,1:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,水缸的事怎樣了?Abbas 會買嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.56,1:10:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他會的,還早嘛,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.58,1:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我懷疑!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.03,1:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.03,1:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好多了老師
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.05,1:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果好多了下午來學校好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.82,1:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該是懶鬼喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.27,1:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著,你的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.74,1:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一點米,讓你媽給你煮些湯喝
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.57,1:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明天來上課
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.77,1:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.54,1:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.88,1:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.06,1:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有事要回去了,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.74,1:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老師, 老師!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.66,1:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我媽給你一些胡桃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.48,1:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要胡桃,拿回去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.25,1:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不拿她會不高興的，連袋子拿去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.77,1:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seyed Yahya什麼時候去城裡買油
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.80,1:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他天氣好些就去.別煩他
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.66,1:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老師給我這些東西: 一袋胡桃,兩封信\N和 200 個拖曼.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.07,1:12:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他說請 Yahya 寄給他母親
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.85,1:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放著吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.39,1:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.41,1:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道人們會怎麼說我...我死了算了,天吶
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.43,1:12:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼面對那些人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.78,1:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 發生什麼事?\N為什麼哭? 太太...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.15,1:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,我不知道 Abbas去哪了\N不知道他是不是鬼迷了心
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.44,1:13:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還是被風暴困住了\N或是水缸打破了?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.75,1:13:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事, 沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.51,1:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他很快會回來的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.08,1:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他會回來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.84,1:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思?他會回來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.82,1:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,傳言難聽的很...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.62,1:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說他拿了錢在城裡花了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.20,1:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說他吃肉串還去看電影...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.73,1:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我的孩子!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.45,1:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會做使我丟臉的事的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.14,1:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,隨他們怎麼說,別聽就是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.13,1:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,隨他們說去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.92,1:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,還有的說他要住在城裡
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.00,1:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有的說他要開店
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.20,1:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有的說他要結婚
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.78,1:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的話真叫我傷心
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.68,1:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我兩天不能出門,因為沒鞋子穿
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.80,1:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 Seyed Reza 那裡想買雙鞋
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.03,1:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說我是拿水缸的錢買的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.52,1:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓那些錢我都數好了讓 Abbas帶去城裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.66,1:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道, 我知道, 妳別難過
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.33,1:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,胡桃給你媽媽了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.60,1:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.85,1:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.91,1:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.09,1:14:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有,沒有什麼問題.別擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.48,1:14:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心?為什麼要擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.32,1:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.92,1:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說胡桃是我偷偷給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.63,1:14:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.83,1:14:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不覺得丟臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.93,1:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.12,1:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,他們還編了歌呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.44,1:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mohammad Ali唱
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.47,1:14:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,唱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.54,1:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果學校要水缸
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.31,1:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,出錢,出無花果
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.84,1:14:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,出胡桃...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.17,1:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老師的媽媽得到胡桃
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.41,1:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他得到所有的錢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.03,1:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有廉恥的人還能怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.28,1:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是穆斯林嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.95,1:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這樣背後說別人的壞話?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.19,1:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 他們的罪會洗清的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.76,1:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能不擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.84,1:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是石頭 我是個人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.38,1:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要弄清楚怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.25,1:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰寫的這無聊東西
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.07,1:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他們丟進我家的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.95,1:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 要知道是誰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.32,1:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是 Moosa,就是那個放羊的.\N他只讀到四年級.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.07,1:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他自稱是村裡的詩人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.94,1:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老師怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.65,1:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼不睡了?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.28,1:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.54,1:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡不著,你睡你的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.67,1:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我都醒著
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.90,1:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看著你直到清晨都沒睡
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.23,1:16:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要煩你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.38,1:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你是為了 Ravar 說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.83,1:16:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別去理他
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.73,1:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你睡你的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.50,1:16:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,請等一下,你要上哪去?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.06,1:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望 Abbas 帶水缸回來時你能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.86,1:17:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.48,1:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看,因為你們老師要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.85,1:17:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你們說了多少他的壞話,\N你們看...多丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.80,1:17:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.02,1:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子是我用自己的錢買的...\N不是水缸的錢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.31,1:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃是我交給他的.他不肯要...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.84,1:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我求他留著
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.70,1:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,幾天前他去 Ebrahymy家看望他
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.10,1:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我親眼看到他襯衫裡藏著一個袋子.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.79,1:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他問我 Ebrahymy家在哪?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.54,1:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你們總有人可以看出
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.60,1:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他為孩子們的付出
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.38,1:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,學校水缸嗎?是我給的結果被你們打破了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.58,1:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,它自己破的別怪我們
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.90,1:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而且,那發酸的水也不可以喝了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.10,1:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的人們,他難過得整夜不能睡
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.94,1:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.07,1:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,讓老師自己說
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.40,1:17:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他畢竟是受教育的明白人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.76,1:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你說誰讓你生氣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.24,1:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫他跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.46,1:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人讓我生氣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.72,1:17:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是厭煩了...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.29,1:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你們接管學校\N我會向教育局報告的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.52,1:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,兩三天內你們就會有新老師
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.16,1:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不會讓你走的\N你要上哪去
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.69,1:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心血都在孩子身上.\N我們也心疼我們的子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.70,1:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也在乎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.82,1:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你就像我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.39,1:18:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的白鬍鬚...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.34,1:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我一句老人言
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.42,1:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聽完你要走再走
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.26,1:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,願神與你同在...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.46,1:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是受過教育的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.53,1:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果背後的耳語
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.96,1:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能動搖人的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.13,1:18:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼那些宗教的先驅們就不會成事了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.21,1:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.01,1:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,賺不到錢了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.57,1:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別生事,要錢是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.98,1:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫他給你錢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.51,1:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓我們傷心
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.63,1:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.15,1:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拿了錢走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.84,1:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.22,1:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拿著.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.10,1:19:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,願神與你同在
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.47,1:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,老師,你別走 別走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.40,1:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,你生氣啦?\N是不是我們做錯了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.69,1:19:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老師,要不要進教室?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.14,1:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,進教室,還問? 老師馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.61,1:19:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們都進教室去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.64,1:19:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,進教室
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.49,1:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.49,1:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們喝水的事我會想辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.87,1:19:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝神